mixin _lessons(lessons)
	#lessons
		.lesson
			h2(class="lesson_title") Buffer Overflow
			a(href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ahUBv0Nvk1Y")
				img(class="lesson_thumb" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ahUBv0Nvk1Y/mqdefault.jpg")
			p(class="lesson_description") This video can help you learn a little bit more about the mechanics behind buffer overflows. It is relatively in depth and includes good examples.
		.lesson
			h2(class="lesson_title") argc/argv
			a(href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aP1ijjeZc24")
				img(class="lesson_thumb" src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/aP1ijjeZc24/mqdefault.webp")
			p(class="lesson_description") Understanding of argc and argv is critical to any c programming, whether or not it is security related. This video outlines how it works in a program and where each part comes from.

